        'Using LI_01_Policy_Portfolio.xlsx — especially the New Business Tracker and Bancassurance Performance tabs — explain why new business value is weakening and whether the bigger challenge is channel productivity, product fit, or customer selection. Distinguish what management can address quickly from what requires a structural response, and state which question the executive committee must answer first. Flag immediate priorities as Red, urgent watchlist items as Amber, and lower-priority items as Green. Present as a RAG table.',
