        'Using LI_03_Actuarial_Policy.docx and the Actuarial Reserve Summary tab in LI_01_Policy_Portfolio.xlsx, identify the capital and reserve questions that BNM and the Board are most likely to raise if current lapse and sales trends persist. Distinguish between earnings strain, reserve adequacy, and business mix risk, and explain which issue would most undermine management credibility if ignored. Flag immediate escalation topics as Red, important follow-ups as Amber, and stable areas as Green. Present as a RAG table.'
