        'Use Researcher in CRITIQUE MODE: ask Researcher to research how life insurers in Malaysia and Indonesia have responded from 2022 to 2025 when bancassurance productivity softened and early-duration lapses rose simultaneously. For at least 3 published case studies, identify the trigger event, the management response within 60 days, and the new business and persistency outcomes 12 months later. Critically, instruct Researcher to self-critique each source, verify every claim against the original publication, and flag any claim it cannot independently verify. Cite every source with publication date.',
